        "experiment_id": 1,
        "reaction_type": "羟基烷基化/烷基化反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydroxyalkylation/alkylation reaction",
        "description": "在PC-180催化剂上，2-甲基呋喃(2-MF)与糠醛进行羟基烷基化/烷基化(HAA)反应，生成5,5′-(呋喃-2-基亚甲基)双(2-甲基呋喃)(1a)。反应条件：50°C, 2小时，催化剂0.10 g，2-MF (1.68 g, 20 mmol)，糠醛 (0.96 g, 10 mmol)。",
        "text_snippet": "These catalysts were very active in the hydroxyalkylation/alkylation (HAA) reactions between 2-methylfuran (2-MF) and furfural. Under mild reaction conditions, the PC-180 catalyst produced a good yield (79.1%) of the HAA product from furfural and 2-MF",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "加氢脱氧反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrodeoxygenation reaction",
        "description": "在Ni/AlPO₄-800催化剂上，对HAA产物1a进行加氢脱氧(HDO)反应，将其转化为C₉–C₁₅柴油和喷气燃料范围烷烃。反应条件：260°C, 4.0 MPa氢气压力, 24小时, Ni/AlPO₄催化剂(0.20 g), 液体原料(1.0 g), 环己烷(30 mL)。",
        "text_snippet": "After hydrodeoxygenation over the Ni/AlPO₄-800 catalyst, these HAA products can be selectively transformed into jet fuel and diesel range branched alkanes.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
  },
